CPOOL

Usage: ^gCPOOL <Dodge> <Body> <Offense>^n

This command is used to quickly set your pools to your desired values.
All three fields must be entered even if you wish to set 0 extra dice.
If more dice are alloted to offense than your skill in the weapon you
are currently wielding then they will be automatically put into the dodge 
pool.

^WSee Also: POOLS, COMBAT POOL, BODY POOL, DODGE POOL^n
